<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<p>
TO SWAP ITEMS: 
</p>
<p>
Inscribe both items(typically weapons or sometimes magic helms) with @w5 
</p>
<p>
make a macro that does w5 when you press, say, F5 
</p>
<p>
Each time you use it, weapons are swapped. 
</p>
<p>
You could have inscripted @5 instead of @w5 but the w means it won't interfer with any other @5 items such as "a scroll of identify {@5}" 
</p>
<p>
Generic use: @w(number) for wear-specific. Won't affect other commands. 
</p>
